<p>The long-form gallery pattern demonstrates a method of displaying a large number of images on a page and makes use of the <a href="http://lokeshdhakar.com/projects/lightbox2">Lightbox JavaScript library</a> to view the images in an immersive experience.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Thumbnail images should be <code>170px x 170px</code>.</li>
  <li>Must only be used within the main content of a long-form page.</li>
  <li>A page can contain multiple galleries.</li>
  <li>There should be no more than 10 images in any one gallery.</li>
  <li>Use <code>data-lightbox="[gallery name]"</code> to group images together for each gallery.</li>
</ul>

